<cb:div type="taisho-notes">
<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0821003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821003">拕＝柁【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0821004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821004">貪＝含【知】</note>
<note n="0821005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821005">想＝相【三】【宮】【聖】【知】＊</note>
<note n="0821006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821006">起＝趣【聖】</note>
<note n="0821007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821007">行＝住【知】</note>
<note n="0821008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821008">名＝能【聖】</note>
<note n="0821009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821009">誡＝戒【三】【宮】【聖】【知】</note>
<note n="0821010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0821010">刀＝力【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0822001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0822001">能＝是【明】</note>
<note n="0822002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0822002">責＝嘖【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0822003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0822003">上＝止【三】【宮】【聖】【知】</note>
<note n="0822004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0822004">得＝德【聖】【知】＊</note>
<note n="0823001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0823001">離＝雜【聖】</note>
<note n="0823002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0823002">於＝如【明】</note>
<note n="0823003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0823003">亦＝示【聖】</note>
<note n="0824001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0824001">等＝第【知】</note>
<note n="0824002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0824002">縛＝纏【宋】【元】【聖】【知】</note>
<note n="0824003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0824003">（病）＋死【聖】</note>
<note n="0825001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0825001">智＝知【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0825002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0825002">弟＝第【三】【宮】【聖】，等【知】</note>
<note n="0825003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0825003">界＝累【聖】【知】</note>
<note n="0825004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0825004">後＝彼【知】</note>
<note n="0825005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0825005">坦＝但【聖】</note>
<note n="0825006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0825006">（一）＋別【宋】【宮】【聖】【知】</note>
<note n="0826001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0826001">如＝知【知】</note>
<note n="0826002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0826002">憎＝增【知】</note>
<note n="0826003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0826003">墮＝隨【聖】</note>
<note n="0826004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0826004">而＝所【三】【宮】【聖】【知】</note>
<note n="0826005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0826005">有少＝少有【三】【宮】【聖】【知】</note>
<note n="0826006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0826006">〔法〕－【元】</note>
<note n="0826007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0826007">深＝染【聖】＊</note>
<note n="0827001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0827001">信＝行【宮】【聖】【知】</note>
<note n="0827002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0827002">廢＝癈【知】＊</note>
<note n="0827003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0827003">此下聖本有光明皇后願文</note>
<note n="0827004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0827004">知本奧書如卷第九十一</note>
</p>
